\begin_layout Chapter
Chapter 1: Shining Lights
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The Luminous built the Dream they draw their Light from over the generations,
 hiding it away in the corners of humanity's shared subconscious.
 Their Light is as fluid and shifting a thing as any other dream.
 Before the Luminous were magical girls, they were the paladins in shining
 armor, the angels with wings of light, the witch in the forest, the village
 shaman.
 All dreaming of a better world, where they and those they love could simply
 live happily.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
In the moment they Blossom, the nascent Hopeful awakens to that shared Dream,
 using its symbols and ideas to build herself a new form and construct your
 ideal identity.
 In that moment, she makes a shard of the Light truly her own power.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Each Hopeful's Light is woven out of three symbols, drawn from the Dream:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Their Luminary forms the foundation of their magic, reflecting their approach
 to the world.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
The Archetype shapes their Dream Form and how they project their Light upon
 the world.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
The Kingdom they are a citizen of in their dreams, reflecting their vision
 of a better world.
 
\end_layout

