In the times before history even began, we looked to the skies for guidance.
 We saw the sun as a shining beacon that watched over all, the moon a mysterious
 guide that shone through the night, and the stars a fountain of mystery
 and wonder.
 So many of our stories were written around those lights...
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
When the lights of heaven no longer suffice, the Hopeful may still be the
 shining protectors and guides of this generation.
 When a Luminous Blossoms, they draw on the stories of those lights and
 use it as a foundation for all the rest of their magic.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
