\begin_layout Itemize
\noindent
Those who pattern their magic after Moonlight become mystical guides, shaping
 the world around them as the moon shapes the tides.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
\noindent
Those who pattern their magic after Starlight become esoteric witches, wielding
 charms and spells as diverse and colorful as the stars themselves.
 
\end_layout

